Reverse and Add
===

Understanding the problem
---
just have to reverse the input number and add it, until you got an
palindrome

Gotchas
---
be carefull with datatype of the input and output number, it will fix
in an unsinged int

Explanation
---
simulate the process, to reverse you can treath it as an string (API handle reverse in java and c++), or 
like a number, and use module or other method

